這個一定就是幕後首腦
逮到他，其他人就跑不掉


1322
01:40:38.281 --> 01:40:43.356
<i>There was something about this kid
that made you want to protect her for life.</i>
這個年輕人
讓你想保護她


1323
01:42:00.733 --> 01:42:02.642
<i>That bullet was meant for me.</i>
那子彈是要射我的


1324
01:42:06.279 --> 01:42:10.407
<i>Maybe this was a long shot,
but I've seen some funny ones pay off.</i>
也許這一次勝算不大，
