01:50:00.266 --> 01:50:02.094
So we have nothing to give you...
我們沒什麼好送你


1375
01:50:02.186 --> 01:50:05.436
but our gratitude, our admiration...
只有我們的感激，我們的敬佩


1376
01:50:06.232 --> 01:50:08.022
and our love.
